ding Bulbasaur, Charmander, Squirtle, Pikachu, and Snorlax. The set costs $425--making it one of the most expensive options in the catalog--but no doubt they look striking and should bring a pop of color to your kitchen.</p><p>The most expensive option is the <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.skimresources.com%3Fid%3D225336X1707200%26xs%3D1%26xcust%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.bokksu.com%2Fcollections%2Fpokemon-le-creuset-collection%2Fproducts%2Fpokemon-le-creuset-cocotte-ronde-hot-pot&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fthis-very-fancy-pokemon-cookware-line-includes-129-mug-999-pot%2F1100-6530105%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Cocotte Ronde: Pikachu Edition</a>. Clocking in at $999, the cast enamel pot is durable, versatile, and absolutely gorgeous with its vibrant nectar coloration and iridescent knob. So whether you're simmering, baking, stir-frying, or steaming, it's a premium companion for all your cooking needs.</p><p>The Pokemon Le Creuset Collection features 12 items. Here's a look at them all.</p><h2>Le Creuset Pokemon Cookware</h2><ul><li><a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.skimresources.com%3Fid%3D225336X1707200%26xs%3D1%26xcust%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.bokksu.com%2Fcollections%2Fpokemon-le-creuset-collection%2Fproducts%2Fpokemon-le-creuset-mini-bowl-4-pieces&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fthis-very-fancy-pokemon-cookware-line-includes-129-mug-999-pot%2F1100-6530105%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Mini Bowls (4 Pieces)</a> -- $270 (<del>$285</del>)</li><li><a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.skimresources.com%3Fid%3D225336X1707200%26xs%3D1%26xcust%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.bokksu.com%2Fcollections%2Fpokemon-le-creuset-collection%2Fproducts%2Fpokemo