            <title><![CDATA[Nintendo Announces New Store That Will Be Open After Switch 2 Reveal]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gamespot.com/articles/nintendo-announces-new-store-that-will-be-open-after-switch-2-reveal/1100-6530101/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f</link>
